{"word":"H4055 - מַד - mad - mad - Armour","slug":"H4055","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מַד</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>mad"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>mad"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Armour"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05D3;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05DE;&#x05D3; - mad  me&#x0302;d</b> - <i>mad, made</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H4058\">H4058</a>; properly <i>extent</i>, that is, <i>height</i>; also a <i>measure</i>; by implication a <i>vesture</i> (as measured); also a <i>carpet: - </i>armour, clothes, garment, judgment, measure, raiment, stature."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4058\">H4058</a>, <a href=\"#/H4059\">H4059</a>, <a href=\"#/H4060\">H4060</a>, <a href=\"#/H4067\">H4067</a>, <a href=\"#/H4081\">H4081</a>, <a href=\"#/H4461\">H4461</a>"}]}